snippet.title: Gearend Trailer - Now Available on Steam and Itch.io!
snippet.description:
Hello! 

Gearend is now available on Steam and itch.io.

https://solarlune.itch.io/gearend
http://store.steampowered.com/app/574500/Gearend/

The OST can also be purchased over on my Bandcamp page here:

https://solarlune.bandcamp.com/

Thank you all very much for helping me make this possible. It's awesome that I've finally finished this project, many years in the making.
